item.dc:creator: @I_Br3ndan_I I Br3ndan I
item.description:
@I_Br3ndan_I wrote:

[quote=“crazycam10, post:5, topic:103969”][quote author=pking4phats link=topic=148714.msg1411970#msg1411970 date=1180733001]
will i still get the keylogger from just having it in my messgae inbox and have read it?
[/quote]
No Not Unless You Download It And Open It,
Then Your Completley Screwed[/quote]

If you have a good anti-virus, it could search for and delete the keylogger as it is, a virus. If all else fails, you should delete the current account you’re using on you’re PC and create a new one. That’s my advice to anyone who has this virus.
